Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别磨蹭  涂鸦先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mr. Doodles
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.31,0:01:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们时间不多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we haven't got all day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得马上去我最爱的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to down to me favorite restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.25,0:01:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来拍我们第一条蟹堡王广告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:14.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we're shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our first ever Krusty Krab commercial
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,广告播完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After this commercial airs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能宾客盈门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll be swarming with customers
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都能感觉到自己在流钱汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can already feel myself sweating money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.23,0:01:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我让章鱼哥来安排拍摄事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I got Squidward organizing the whole thing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,artsy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.57,0:01:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(262,272)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好贵的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This looks expensive
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.53,0:01:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.44,0:01:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.44,0:01:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不滚你们就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move it or lose it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.16,0:01:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in Neptune's name is going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在拍广告啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're making the commercial, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在就是在乱丢我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you're doing is throwing away me money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.58,0:01:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都交代过你只租绝对有必要的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you to rent only what's absolutely necessary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,场上东西全都有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all necessary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这堆没用的垃圾是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what's all this useless junk?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是第28幕要用的没用垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the useless junk for scene 28
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你要怎么解释那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, how do you explain that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二家蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A second Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王  大家都得有替补演员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, everyone needs an understudy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you got me there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可要他来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why do we need him?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍广告压力非常大  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This job gets very stressful, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  全都给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, get lost, all of you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.18,0:02:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.10,0:02:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scram
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上给我滚  死骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, you moochers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, keep moving
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.23,0:02:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is just great
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下拍摄团队一个都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we've got no crew to make the commercial
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道什么啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最便宜的拍摄团队就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got the cheapest crew in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说到他  那小东西哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, where is that little barnacle?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm down here, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说活埋自己能协助拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward said I could help by burying myself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit fooling and come on out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你来当广告演员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you to be in the commercial
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当蟹堡王广告演员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the Krusty Krab commercial?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.12,0:02:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But-
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别扯淡了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't throw your buts at me, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间很紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got a timetable to keep
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,广告今晚就放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This thing airs tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.28,0:03:00.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:00.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.96,0:03:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地买了个黄金时段的广告位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a sweet deal on a prime-time slot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,凌晨三点二十八分
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快开播了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我也很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got butterflies, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史上史上最兴奋的事马上就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the most exciting thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ever happen in the history of history
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗快看  开播了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Gary, it's on
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小珍  我出了个很严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jen, I've got a real problem
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么问题呢  艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your problem, Amy?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手上有这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got all this money
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道要怎么花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I don't know what to do with it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我还饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's that coming from?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yippee
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Amy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的小问题我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard all about your little problem
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来帮你解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm here to help
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个地方正是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, we're at none other than
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,392)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诞生了举世闻名的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home of the world famous
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七大洋里最美味的食物非它莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's only the most mouth-watering
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,appetizing food in the seven seas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在那边  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There I am, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There I am
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先从新鲜的肉饼开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We start with a fresh patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,香烤多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grilled and juicy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加上酥脆的海底蔬菜与奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Add some crisp undersea veggies and cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再配上神秘酱料  以及面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Topped off with secret sauce and some buns
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.91,0:04:21.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:21.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voila
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想来个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡好不好吃  大小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you liking them Krabby Patties, girls?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看小蜗  我又出镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Gary, there I am again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又多了两位满意的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two more satisfied customers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, why don't you come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.82,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天就给自己买个蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and have yourself a Krabby Patty today?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come spend your money here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚是我一生中最棒的60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the best 60 seconds of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, time for bed
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该去我最爱的地方最我最爱的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go do my favorite thing at my favorite place
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top of the morning, Oldster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我昨晚看电视看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw you on TV last night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,452)}麦麸片
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新麦麸片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New Bran Flakes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新浓厚风味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bold new taste
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麦麸片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bran Flakes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我看广告看到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you were on a commercial
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他居然认得我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He recognized me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  麦麸片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Bran Flakes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那麦片盒真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a nice cereal box
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是上电视的那位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Weren't you that guy on TV?"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我就是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Yes, I am that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能注意到我真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How kind of you to notice"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是昨晚上电视的那位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Weren't you that guy on the television last night?"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Yes, that was me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.43,0:05:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's quite all right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,396)}你好  我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Spongebob"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我声名远扬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting recognized all over
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后大家多半就要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:05:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,people are going to start doing stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮忙开门什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like holding doors open for
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  我不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, sir, I'm flattered
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没闻出你要进的味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't smell anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你走吧  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on your way, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给个餐巾纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get a napkin?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, of course, dear sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次有事随时找我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And next time, feel free to approach me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在房间对面问话一定很没面子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be so degrading to ask from across the room
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问这张纸得给谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who am I making this bad boy out to?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我尾鳍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To my tail fin
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己拿算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱼老日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,F-I-N
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写好了  贵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There we are, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来他太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shyness got the best of him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经签好名了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got one already made out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,品鉴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(668,248)}给我尾鳍\N爱你的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我尾鳍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"To my tail fin"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我就是上电视的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am that guy on TV
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.83,0:06:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班期间请大家不要拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, good people, no photos at work
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄酱在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the ketchup
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:56.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772,180)}调料区
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是拍一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe just one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.01,0:06:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,林波舞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Limbo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now the
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jet pilot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I need you to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去把厕所擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in there and scrub the head
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别一直犯老毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and stop acting so predictable
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怀才不遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So misunderstood
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, good people
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即便最明亮的明星也会黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even the brightest of stars grow weary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亦不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I am no exception
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但只需小憩一刻  我将再度闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I will shine again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after a quick break in my quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你昨晚有看到葛兰迪麦粉鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Were you able to catch Glandy McPinkfish
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出演比目鱼侠这部剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on Flounderman last night?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看  他演得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, how was he?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然本来就知道他演技好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew this guy's acting was good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但头一回发现他唱功特强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but his singing is phenomenal
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摆摊的  我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tell you, Vender
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他能出个人专辑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if that guy was to cut a solo record
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定会热销
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it would be a hit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个人专辑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Solo record
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我开除他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, if I fire him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让接班的工作量翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make his successor do twice the work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just you, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厕所最好已经擦漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those heads better be beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很漂亮  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They are, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的脑袋也一样漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and so is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要跟你放点话  小螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now I got to lay something on you, Krabs baby
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一要你放的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing you better lay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是烤架上的肉饼  小厨子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is some patties on the grill, fry boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我做不来  蟹老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take that gig, Krabber
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那段厨师生涯已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That phase of my career is over
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.08,0:08:13.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:13.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an entertainer now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in blazes are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  先跳出思维定势思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Krabs, let's think outside the box for a second
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,广告已经作古了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Commercials are old hat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大众要的是音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people want music
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要能改变命运的话早变了  蟹老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I could change fate, I would, Krabsie
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我内心深处是一位演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm an entertainer deep down
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位公众人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a people's person
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们立场一致  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're on the same page here, aren't we?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的油烟一定把你熏昏头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, those krabby fumes must have got to your head
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去借章鱼哥的防毒面具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Borrow Squidward's gas mask
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借完马上回来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then get right back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd understand
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你发话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for the start
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.64,0:08:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没混杂着这么怪的两种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never felt such a strange combination
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一边遗憾  一边消化不良
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of pity and indigestion
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还要害我们在这傻站多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep us standing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.24,0:09:05.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底要目瞪口呆傻站着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you just going to stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like a half-wit, mouth agape
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是把大家的餐都做好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or are you going to fill these people's orders?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pipe down, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家样子都很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This crowd looks angry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用让他们再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not going to wait any longer
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上迅速就把大家想要的送上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I better give them what they need and fast
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think so, too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然老螃蟹会把我们俩都开除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or Krabs will fire both of us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多想了下  让客人继续等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On second thought, keep them waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做不到  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No can do, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人要的是娱乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These people demand entertainment
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娱什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enter what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How you doing, folks?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很饿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就不成问题  女士们细菌们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no problem, ladies and germs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为海绵宝宝要来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause Spongebob is here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满足大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to satisfy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪你要来这吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eating here was your idea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.00,0:09:40.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我管这首叫  条纹毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:40.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to call this little number "Striped Sweater"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.17,0:09:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最适合穿条纹毛衣的时节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The best time to wear a striped sweater
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是每分每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.93,0:09:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它的衣领翻得特别高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One with a collar, turtleneck
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the kind
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.73,0:09:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为当你穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause when you're wearing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're starving
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.03,0:09:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:09:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,special sweater
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  客人都不满足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, this crowd is insatiable
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不然你就回厨房去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you get back in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿点肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and grab some patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给大家想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give them what they came here for
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.04,0:10:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杂耍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Juggling
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人想要一边杂耍一边听玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They want juggling and jokes at the same time?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太难伺候了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tough crowd
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他又干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what's he doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.42,0:10:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车在血库三里外抛锚的吸血鬼叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you call a vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whose car breaks down three miles from a blood bank?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A cab
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们快没胃口了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're losing our appetites
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  有个尼姑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's a nun
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宇航员  还有吹风机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an astronaut, and a hairdryer
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一次最多只能耍三块
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the most I can juggle is three
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但表演不能停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the show must go on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的生涯结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My career is over
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.77,0:11:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么多年摸爬滚打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All those years clawing my way up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跨越前人  全都白搭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the people I've stepped on, wasted
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直就在等这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what we've been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.39,0:11:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好像很喜欢我把肉饼放烤架上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They seem to like it when I put this patty on the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一幕多半还能抢救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may be able to save this act yet
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺其自然  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll with it, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,roll with it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's more where that came from, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直都很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's what we wanted all along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  可是得怎么跟进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working, but how do I follow it up?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要当机立断  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think on your feet, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.80,0:11:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走到这步全都是靠当机立断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what got you this far
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,704)}面包
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.20,0:11:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buns
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然事情难办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a stretch
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但总有一刻必须挑战极限
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we all got to try to push the envelope sometime
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家觉得这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, folks, how do you like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开辟新天地了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm breaking new ground
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来躁起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get edgy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want onions
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备看压轴好戏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for the grand finale?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  看来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Spongebob, looks like
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总算发现自己的使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you finally found your calling
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll say
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴我能为这个放弃厨师工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I gave up fry cooking for this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.72,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(364,354)}一角钱的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:27.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz25.1\pos(325.802,486)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(403.802,524)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(411.802,298)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(319.802,330)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(499.802,666)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,464)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的打烊时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closing time at The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,51  52  53
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,51, 52, 53
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,29  30  31
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,29, 30, 31
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  能走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, can we please go now?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们某位更加忠诚的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps one of our more loyal workers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计可以帮你讲明白员工守则
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can enlighten you on company policy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王员工守则第二修订版
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab Employee Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Second Revised Edition
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第35页第19节3a款
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,page 35, section 19, clause 3a states
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体员工须留在蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"All staff must remain on the premises
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直至当天的收入全部清点完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until the day's receipts are fully accounted for"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那样很过分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's not fair
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.22,0:12:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第3b款
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:56.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clause 3b
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,业主留有过分对待员工的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The proprietor reserves the right to be unfair"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真会答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teacher's pet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数数看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五  十
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,five, ten
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,25  蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,25, blue
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苹果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,applesauce
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来井然有序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything looks to be in order
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.26,0:13:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My dime
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别的一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me special dime
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赚的第一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The first dime I ever made
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直放收银机最里面图吉利的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always keep it at the back of the register for luck
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never seen it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared to say that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双手放在形意舞季刊上面发誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your hand on a stack of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Interpretive Dance Quarterlies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,216)}舞蹈季刊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你胡说八道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我并没有针对哪个谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't saying nothing that would matter to anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非那个谁愿意来测谎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who'd be willing to take a lie detector test
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你话中有话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're saying something
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heavens to Betsy, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯只是我的幸运一毛钱不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that me lucky dime's gone missing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚好你整天都在负责收银
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you've been working the register all day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要让我背锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you accusing me of something?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依我看  有三种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the way I see it, there are three possibilities
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you stole it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you stole it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or three
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you stole it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没偷你的宝贝一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't take your precious dime
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,触手拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show me your tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要看到你吸盘没东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to see empty suction cups
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See them?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.44,0:14:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能那么整我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can't do that to me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your boss
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不是了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not anymore, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你犯下大错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're making a big mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mistake?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我唯一犯下的大错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only mistake I ever made
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是在蟹堡王浪费大好年华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was wasting my life at The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可大家来蟹堡王都会快快乐乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But a visit to The Krusty Krab makes everyone happy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么能比微笑服务更棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what could be better than serving up smiles?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上西天什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being dead or anything else
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道这事让你反应这么强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never knew you felt so strongly about this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我也拦不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I can't stop you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面是个严寒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's a cold, cold world out there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.33,0:14:53.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸福不是白送的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's going to serve you happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a silver platter
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费试吃品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free sample?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.07,0:14:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.99,0:14:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能来一块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have one?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之  我想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I just want you to know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果碰上麻烦  就来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you ever get in trouble, come find me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause you and me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就像兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're like brothers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是更亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only closer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我不需要你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, I don't need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经准备好释放潜力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am ready to unlock my potential
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能成为我想成为的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can become anything I set my mind to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以当橄榄球球员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could be a football player
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者国王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or a king
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or a spaceman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者太空上打橄榄球的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or a football playing king in space
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还长了个胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a mustache
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒是让我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, that reminds me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打相识那天  我一直有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's something I've been wanting to say to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since the day we met
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下次你见到我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time you see me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.33,0:15:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全城都会对我卑躬屈膝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this town will be eating out of the palm of my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赏点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spare change?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赏点钱  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spare change, ma'am?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.30,0:15:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们从前是同事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We used to work together
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你这几天都住哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So where you living these days?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问是章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这签字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sign here please
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nowhere
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  那你近况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, and what have you been doing with yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我先猜猜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait, let me guess
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你一直都在留胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you've been working on that mustache
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣着破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tattered clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭气熏天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the awful smell
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是橄榄球球员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a football player
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A spaceman
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太空上打橄榄球的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A football playing king in space?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个失败者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a loser
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没了工作  没了家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've lost my job, my home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everything
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连画都没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even your paintings?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人愿意买画  我就只能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody would take them, so I had to eat them
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.83,0:16:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以来跟我住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can come live with me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就睡我床上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sleep in my bed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我找到工作马上走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, but just till I get a job
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最多住个一两天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One day, two days tops
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.13,0:17:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别见外  需要住多久就住多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, you stay as long as you need to
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  我的小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, my little angel
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要养精蓄锐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll need to build up your strength again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就帮你做了大自助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I laid out a big buffet for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在床上吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in bed, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞机来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes the plane
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's really nice of you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能在我需要的时候帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to help me in my time of need
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽量不拖累你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try not to be a burden
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要我帮你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else I can do for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.04,0:17:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了  你已经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, you've already
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:01.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1064,440)}针灸
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滋养破碎的心灵可多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nourishing a broken spirit is a lot of work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm bushed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过做好事还是让我很舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still, it feels nice to do good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我倒杯水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can I get a glass of water?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.06,0:18:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.35,0:18:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能给我再盖条毛毯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, can I get some more blankets?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你忘记关灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, you forgot to turn out the light
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.75,0:18:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥才没有吃白食
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is not a freeloader
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肯定不会占我便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he would never take advantage of me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,三周后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.91,0:19:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是不容易重拾信心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just having a hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,getting his confidence back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,很多月后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他马上就要有重大进展了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's close to a breakthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,过了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,老旁白已经等烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,于是只好雇了个新旁白
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道他还是没去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know he still isn't looking for work
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用你再强调
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't rub it in
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.18,0:19:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我的柠檬水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, where's my lemonade?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么没穿制服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why aren't you in uniform?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你早该来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about time you got here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喝吧  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, your majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我不能喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't drink that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你瞎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you blind?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.61,0:19:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这柠檬里面有三颗籽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That lemon has three seeds in it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是奇数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's an odd number
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.33,0:19:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带奇数的我都吃不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't eat anything odd numbered
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  那我挑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll just take it out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.39,0:20:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它已经被坏柠檬污染了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's already contaminated by the bad lemon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It won't work
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.03,0:20:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里有两样东西坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's two things in this house that won't work
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就去修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then go fix them
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.81,0:20:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两样东西坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two things that won't work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:19.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(844,920)}不工作
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,柠檬水我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改喝汤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want soup instead
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't move
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是字母汤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's alphabet soup
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特制的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it special
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478,812)}找工作
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浓缩罐头汤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Condensed soup from a can
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你倒是坏了我的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you've ruined my appetite
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我拿点书报什么的看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go fetch me something to read
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个看不看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,156)}招聘启事
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get that away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.53,0:20:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对印刷油墨过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know I'm allergic to newsprint
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把报纸从我手上拍飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, when you swatted that newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:56.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out of my hands
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想起来我有个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it reminded me of something a friend of mine did
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班也这样过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at his job
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,4:00
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我演故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for my stories
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你懒懒散散的  节目还会照样放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they won't hold the show while you laze around
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To my job
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have a job?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛会没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又不是某些不为他人着想的懒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not some lazy, inconsiderate jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整天赖在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who lays in bed all day
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我可以上哪找到这种工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, where can I get one of these jobs?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.05,0:21:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绿色  还长六只触手的那就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially if you're green and have six tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  我马上就去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'm going to go look for one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就不用占我朋友便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can stop mooching off my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们回归正常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they can get back to their lives
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又不看这部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't my show
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  遥控器坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, the remote control's broken
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我过来修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get over here and fix it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有更好的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a better idea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然打电话找专职工作的来修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't I call someone whose job it is to fix it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know why?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为要把工作做好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because when I need a job done
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.26,0:21:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要找专职工作的来负责工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get someone with a job to do that job
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.83,0:22:06.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给儿童基金会捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:06.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Donate to the children's fund?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.21,0:22:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿童有替我干什么没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have children ever done for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要回你的一毛钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want your dime back?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在章鱼哥能回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now Squidward can come back, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.52,0:22:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是我的第一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't my first dime
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.93,0:22:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就再多收点一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then have some more dimes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got plenty of them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的第一毛钱不能用价格来衡量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't put a price on me first dime
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我也不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can't forgive
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个偷我钱的毛贼章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that thieving bilge rat Squidward for stealing it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  你这个小气螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen you crustaceous cheapskate
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.42,0:22:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥一直借住我家  快把我逼疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's been living at my house driving me crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.88,0:22:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你却只因一毛破钱就不把他雇回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're not going to hire him back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all because of a stupid dime?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.98,0:22:35.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:35.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的第一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me first dime
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.59,0:22:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dimey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.98,0:22:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不会失去你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never lose you again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那居然是一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a dime?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.92,0:22:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很早就在做生意了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been in business a long time, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.96,0:22:45.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:45.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥没偷那一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if Squidward never stole the dime
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就表示他能回来工作了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he can come back to work, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我和一毛钱好好独处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let the dime and me have our privacy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  你能回来真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Squidward, it's good to have you back
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能回来确实很好  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's kind of good to be back, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all water under the bridge now
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.20,0:23:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I agree, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.64,0:23:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定也不是故意要乱放我一毛钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you didn't mean to misplace me dime
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.28,0:23:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在胡说八道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显是你把一毛钱放我裤子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's obvious that you put the dime in me pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一毛钱可不会平白无故飞裤子里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dimes just don't fly into people's pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要让我背锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you accusing me of something?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.18,0:23:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依我看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the way I see it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.44,0:23:23.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有三种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:23.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there are three possibilities
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.78,0:23:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.24,0:23:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你放我裤子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you put the dime in me pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.89,0:23:26.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:26.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你放我裤子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you put the dime in me pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.94,0:23:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or three
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.76,0:23:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你放我裤子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you put the dime in me pants
